snippet.title: [Custom Maid 3D 2] Fallin' Love (KINMOZA! x A Channel x Oreimo x Watamote)
snippet.description:
Custom Maid 3D 2 Dance 
Featuring characters I made to look like...
Alice, Shinobu and Karen from Kiniro Mosaic
Run, Yuko, and Nagi from A Channel
Kirino, Ayase, and Kanako from Oreimo
